name: Reactive Wave
description:
Inspire us to be more responsive to the current situation during the Covid 19 pandemic.

Inspired during the current pandemic. We as creative humans continue to seek innovation even though we are constrained by current conditions, free ourselves with unlimited creativity, collaborating with others is the solution.

Staying enthusiastic, creative and responsive is the key to passing this pandemic, so that people around us will be inspired by positive things.
I hope this pandemic will end quickly and life will return to normal.
